Title: Who Would Mess with Me Now?
---
A magnificent force I have become, having aligned myself with Truth.

Who would mess with me now?

Only a lucky idiot.

So, go ahead. Egg my house, or steal some fruit from that pear tree in my
  backyard.

That would be a good idea, to imbibe something I have tended, like these
  playful word.
